query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(b1 so_user) NoMergeJoin(account b1 so_user b2) */ select count(account.display_name)
from badge AS b1
inner join so_user AS so_user
on b1.site_id = so_user.site_id AND b1.user_id = so_user.id AND b1.name = 'Publicist'
inner join account AS account
on account.id = so_user.account_id AND account.website_url <> ''
inner join badge AS b2
on b2.site_id = so_user.site_id AND b2.user_id = so_user.id AND b2.date > b1.date + '10 months'::interval AND b2.name = 'Publicist';
